;B[qs]LB[rr:1][rs:2][qq:3][qp:4][ps:5][qs:6]C[Dia.1 Bik (mutual life)

When White plays 1 it's clear he hasn't thought things through.  Black can play at 2 and even if White throws in at 3 he can double back and connect at 6 and come out okay.  This ends up being Bik.  We need to change our game plan.
\lang1042\f1\fs18

