;B[ss]LB[rs:1][qs:2][qq:3][rr:4][qp:5][ss:6]C[Dia.2 Pae

After the exchange of White 1 for Black 2, White 3 is a mistake in move order.  Black will protect at 4 and When White takes the two stones, Black will start the Pae.  This is not good for White, he can capture outright.
