;W[rr]LB[qq:1][qp:2][rs:3][qs:4][rr:5]C[Dia.3 Correct / Eye vs. no eye

The trick is to throw in first throw in at 1 and then wait to play the diagonal move of White 3.  This is the correct move order.  There is no way for Black to retaliate.  White 5 makes a solid eye, so now Black dies.  This is a case of "eye vs. no eye".
\lang1042\f1\fs18
